import Publish from './assets/publishImage.webp'
import Retrieve from './assets/retrieveImage.webp'
import Manage from './assets/blob.svg'

const NodeList2 = [
    {
        title: "Publish data",
        sub: "Publish transaction data to Celestia’s DA network.",
        button: "Submit data to Celestia",
        image: Publish
    },
    {
        title: "Retrieve data",
        sub: "Retrieve transaction data from Celestia’s DA network.",
        button: "Retrieve data from Celestia",
        image: Retrieve
    },
    {
        title: "Manage Tia wallet",
        sub: "Generate a Celestia wallet to store Tia and pay for publishing transaction data to Celestia.",
        button: "Setup wallet",
        image: Manage
    }
]

export default NodeList2
